videos.description: In a back-and-forth battle, Lexie Brown drops 19 points and dishes out five assists while Rebecca Greenwell scores 19 of her own, to help No. 16 Duke past No. 18 Oregon State 72-65.
videos.headline: Duke comes out on top over Oregon State
